cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use EvictVC in your research, please cite the paper below."
title: "EvictVC: Evictable Vector Commitments"
abstract: >-
  A vector-commitment primitive supporting permanent, policy-checked deletion of
  committed positions with a tamper-evident deletion history, for verifiable LLM
  inference under KV-cache eviction. Includes a Python reference implementation and
  a high-performance Rust backend over BLS12-381.
